<h3><b>How it creates value for your trading:</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">MoneyFlare creates value by reducing the manual burden of market monitoring, strategy setup, and trade execution. Instead of asking users to build complex models or manage every trade themselves, it focuses on automated participation, real-time opportunity capture, strategy execution, and managed AI quantitative trading workflows.</span></p>
